revision.text:
'''Agrarian structure''' is the pattern of [[land]] (area group) distribution among [[landholders]] ([[agriculture|agricultural]] households).<ref>T. Ludewigs, A. D’Antona, E. S. Brondizio, and  S. Hetrick. 2009. Agrarian structure and land-cover change along the lifespan of three colonization areas in the Brazilian Amazon.World Development, Vol 37, No 8, p. 1349.</ref><ref>[http://www.agrojournal.org/20/05-03.pdf M. Pietrzak and D. Walczak. 2014. The Analysis of the Agrarian Structure in Poland with the Special Consideration of the Years 1921 and 2002, Bulgarian Journal of Agricultural Science, Vol 20, No 5, pp. 1018.]</ref>

